summary: Completed comprehensive testing of marketplace digital menu application. All core functionality working correctly including customer menu browsing, cart management, inquiry submission, and admin dashboard operations.
passed_tests: Backend API: All 13 endpoints working (GET menu items, categories, search, filter, admin login, CRUD operations, inquiries)
Customer View: Menu display with images, titles, descriptions, categories, prices, and discount badges
Search Functionality: Successfully filters items by title/description
Category Filtering: Correctly filters by Services, Digital, Marketing, Design categories
Cart Management: Add items, update quantities, calculate totals with discounts
Inquiry Form: Customer information input and validation
Inquiry Submission: Successfully creates inquiries with cart items and totals
Admin Login: Authentication with valid/invalid credentials
Admin Dashboard: Menu items management (view, add, edit)
Admin Inquiries: View customer inquiries with complete details
Multiple Variants: Up to 5 variants per item with different prices
Discount System: Percentage discounts applied correctly to pricing
Responsive Design: Clean white background with black and gold styling
